ich brings man more into the world of sound than of sight.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2020) 0aLanguage and languagesxPhilosophy. 0aLogos (Christian theology) 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aWalsh, Mary Roth, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYUP eBook Package 2014-2016z978311053800740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300204636423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300204636.jpg  a978-3-11-053800-7  YUP eBook Package 2014-2016c2014d2016  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles